Reviewing U S Concrete (USCR) & James Hardie Industries PLC. (JHX)

					Posted by Danessa Lincoln on Jul 17th, 2017 // No Comments 




U S Concrete (NASDAQ: USCR) and James Hardie Industries PLC. (NYSE:JHX) are both construction companies, but which is the superior investment? We will contrast the two businesses based on the strength of their risk, institutional ownership, profitabiliy, dividends, valuation, analyst recommendations and earnings. 
